### Test API endpoints for LoRa Gateway
### Sử dụng với REST Client extension trong VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get system status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/status

### Get all nodes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/nodes

### Get specific node
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/nodes/KHO_A

### Get history (last 100 records)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history?limit=100

### Get history for specific node
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history?nodeId=KHO_A&limit=50

### Get history for specific date
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history?nodeId=KHO_A&date=2025-12-09&limit=200

### Get history for date and time range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history?nodeId=KHO_A&date=2025-12-09&startTime=08:00:00&endTime=18:00:00

### Get today's daily statistics for all nodes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/daily-stats

### Get all daily statistics for specific node
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/daily-stats/KHO_A

### Get daily statistics for specific node and date
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/daily-stats/KHO_A?date=2025-12-09

### Turn relay ON
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/control/relay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target": "KHO_A",
  "relay": true
}

### Turn relay OFF
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/control/relay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target": "KHO_A",
  "relay": false
}

### Switch to auto mode
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/control/relay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target": "KHO_A",
  "auto": true
}

### Control all nodes
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/control/relay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target": "ALL",
  "relay": true
}
